data.description: 100% USDA FINANCING AVAILABLE AS WELL AS POSSIBLE DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE WHICH MIGHT GET YOU IN THIS HOME WITH LITTLE TO ZERO OUT OF POCKET!! This is one of the cutest, coolest, and most well-maintained homes out here. I can't find a thing not to like about it. Per Bay County, home has an effective year of 2012, due to upgrades. This home is COMPLETELY FURNISHED and 100% TURNKEY & MOVE-IN READY! Everything you see, ALL CONTENTS, is what conveys. Enjoyable neighborhood, just a very short distance to the beach by foot, car, or golf cart. Both bedrooms are large & have double closets. Great open floor plan. Permitted and enclosed BONUS ROOM (theater room+office+laundry) plus kitchen nook that leads to the delightful back porch and partially shaded spacious backyard. Previous owner spent over $50,000 in updates. Open living space, quartz counter tops, new appliances, ceramic tile flooring, and SOME OF THE MOST UPDATED SMART HOME TECHNOLOGY FEATURES! (Check out the bathroom shower!) The solar panels should keep your bill LOW, LOW, LOW. Golf cart community, minutes to 30A, Pier Park, and the most beautiful emerald-green waters and white-sand beaches you'll find anywhere in the world. See this home Right Now! You're going to LOVE it! Move yourself in for some relaxing beach living, or rent it to some snow birds 6 months or longer.
